data.text: "I want to talk to support" "Connect me to customer service" "Can I speak to a representative?" "I need help from support" "How do I contact support?" "Talk to a human" "Contact customer care" "Get me a support agent" "I need assistance from customer support" "Can you connect me with support?" "Help me talk to customer service" "I want to chat with support" "Is there a way to reach support?" "Can I talk to a live person?" "Put me in touch with customer care"
